# VITE/VUE/TAILWIND Crypto Web3 Project

This is a sample crypto web3 project built using Vite, Vue, and TailwindCSS. The application allows users to log in using a web3 wallet, among other features. 

## Setup and Configuration

### 1. WalletConnect Integration

Before starting the application, you need to integrate it with [WalletConnect](https://walletconnect.com/). Add your `projectId` from WalletConnect to the following section in the code:

```javascript
const projectId = '';

2. Installation

Make sure you have Node.js and npm installed. If not, you can download and install them from here.

Then, navigate to the project directory and install the required packages:
npm install

3. Running the Project

After successfully installing the required packages, you can run the application using:
npm run dev

The application will be accessible at http://localhost:3000 or the respective port displayed in your terminal.
Important Note

This application is a composite of various components sourced and adapted from the web. As such, it's important to note that redirects, further component integrations, and other specifics need to be set up and managed by the user.
License and Usage

This is a sample website, and its code can be used as a starting point for further development. However, ensure you have the rights to use any external components or libraries that might be included.
